N . Ireland police probe kick - boxer ' s match death . Norther Ireland police on Monday investigated the death of a kick boxer who collapsed and died in the ring in front of his family on Friday . Sean McBride , 18 , collapsed at the end of a bout in the town of Dungannon and did not regain consciousness . He died in a Belfast hospital on Sunday , his family said . His parents and three sisters were at the bout , which featured the hybrid sport which mixes karate - style kicking and conventional boxing in gloves . 
